These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
There are 6 different nationalities: italian, polish, japanese, turkish, dutch, thai
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, house, jazz, r&b, rock, soul
 1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the italian##1
 2. the polish is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 3. the polish is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
 4. the fan of soul is not to the left of the japanese##8
 5. the thai is somewhere to the right of the fan of rock##5
 6. the fan of rock is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the thai##7
 7. the italian is not to the left of the fan of jazz##8
 8. the dutch is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 9. the thai is on the left or right of the dutch##3
10. the fan of classical is not to the left of the turkish##8
11. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
12. the polish is on the right of the turkish##1
13. the japanese is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
14. the thai is somewhere between the fan of house and the japanese##7
15. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
16. the dutch is not the fan of r&b##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Nationality           | turkish | polish | italian | dutch | thai | japanese |
| Music-Genre   | classical | jazz    | house  | rock  | r&b            | soul  |

