.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, british, canadian, polish, spanish
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: indie, salsa, dubstep, country, electronic, jazz
 1. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 2. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
 3. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 4. the fan of dubstep is not to the left of the argentine##8
 5. the british is somewhere to the left of the fan of jazz##5
 6. the spanish is on the left or right of the british##3
 7. the fan of indie is somewhere to the right of the british##5
 8. the canadian is not to the right of the canadian##8
 9. the american is somewhere to the right of the british##5
10. the fan of country is on the far right##1
11. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the polish and the fan of dubstep##7
12. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
13. the spanish is between the fan of electronic and the fan of jazz##2
14. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
15. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the american##7
16. the fan of electronic is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
17. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the right of the fan of electronic##5
18. the polish is the fan of salsa##1
19. the fan of dubstep is not the american##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
| Nationality   | polish   | british | spanish    | canadian      | argentine | american |
| Music-Genre         | salsa | electronic  | indie | jazz | dubstep   | country  |

