.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-4::.
There 6 different types of food: eggplant, pineapple, pomegranate, radish, tomato, zucchini
There are 6 different nationalities: turkish, french, russian, british, german, pakistani
 1. the british is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
 2. the russian is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 3. the person eating zucchini is between the turkish and the person eating eggplant##2
 4. the person eating radish is in an even position##4
 5. the person eating zucchini is somewhere between the person eating tomato and the french##7
 6. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
 7. the russian is on the left or right of the british##3
 8. the german is not to the left of the person eating zucchini##8
 9. the french is somewhere to the left of the german##5
10. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
11. the german is somewhere to the left of the british##5
12. the turkish is somewhere between the pakistani and the person eating zucchini##7
13. the pakistani is not to the right of the russian##8
14. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
15. the pakistani is in an even position##4
16. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
17. the french is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |      6      |
| Food    | eggplant | zucchini    | tomato     | radish  | pineapple    | pomegranate |
| Nationality   | french  | german | turkish | pakistani | russian | british     |

