.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-5::.
There 6 different types of food: peas, avocado, garlic, potato, pomegranate, kale
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, bike, helicopter, jet-ski, roller, train
 1. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person eating potato##8
 2. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
 3. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 4. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 5. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person driving the helicopter is the person eating garlic##1
 7. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 8. the person eating avocado is not to the left of the person eating potato##8
 9. the person eating avocado is in an even position##4
10. the person eating potato is on the right of the person driving the train##1
11. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
12. the person eating kale is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |   3    |    4     |     5      |     6     |
| Food   | kale | potato | pomegranate | peas | garlic    | avocado |
| Transport     | train   | airplane  | bike   | jet-ski  | helicopter | roller    |

