6 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, aristoff, swisher, bluemaster, montecristo, dannemann
 1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the montecristo-smoker and the swisher-smoker##7
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 3. the montecristo-smoker is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 4. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5
 5. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking tea and the swisher-smoker##2
 6. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the swisher-smoker##7
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
 8. the dannemann-smoker is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking tea##7
10. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4     |   5   |   6    |
| Beverage      | 7up    | lemonade | soy-milk | tea       | fanta | coffee |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | aristoff  | montecristo      | prince | dannemann  | swisher   |

