There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, lemonade, milk, sprite
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: lily, poppy, aconite, begonia, amaryllis, azalea
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person who growspoppy##7
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is not the person drinking milk##6
 4. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 5. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
 6. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person who growsazalea##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person who growspoppy##5
 9. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
10. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person who growslily##5
11. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
12. the person who growslily is not to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##8
13. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
14. the person who growslily is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
15. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
16. the person who growslily is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
17. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |   3    |  4   |      5      |   6    |
| Beverage   | milk     | lemonade  | sprite | 7up  | almond-milk | juice  |
| Flower       | lily | aconite | azalea | amaryllis | poppy | begonia |

