.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-19::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: crime, fantasy, horror, sports, superhero, time-travel
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daisy, iris, rose, poppy, balloon-flower, marigold
 1. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
 2. the person who growsdaisy is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the person who growsiris##8
 9. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person who growsiris##5
10. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
11. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
12. the person who growsrose is not to the right of the person watching crime movies##8
13. the person who growsrose is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8
14. the person who growspoppy is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8
15. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
16. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
17. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8
18. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the person watching sports movies##5
19. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the right of the person who growsrose##8

.:: Answer ::.
