.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-20::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, drama, musical, scientific, spy
6 different games are played: poker, monopoly, bridge, snooker, go, canasta
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 2. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8
 3. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
 4. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
 5. the person playing snooker is not to the left of the person watching adventure movies##8
 6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
 8. the person playing go is not the person watching musical movies##6
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
10. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
11. the person watching scientific movies is not the person playing snooker##6
12. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
13. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
14. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
15. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
16. the person playing canasta is the person watching scientific movies##1
17. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
18. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
19. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
20. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
21. the person playing canasta is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |     4     |     5      |   6   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | comedy | musical | drama     | scientific | spy   |
| Game   | snooker      | bridge | monopoly    | poker | canasta     | go |

 